        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Here’s a fun challenge for the smart business professional (or savvy wordsmith):",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Make a list of your current service offerings and write a paragraph or two about each of them.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Shorten it to a few sentences. Then two. Then one.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Take your sentence and cut it in half. Edit it and revise it and change the words until you get it down to 60 characters or fewer.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Tough? You bet it is.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But it is a great way to articulate what you actually do.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "To work around the temptation to complicate things and use obtuse language to articulate your point. To write clearly. Free of ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "drivel",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
